tool_description:
SiphonAI Search Result API
Use SiphonAI's Search Result API to get Google search results in milliseconds. Use these to build many types of software that require search results, such as marketing or SEO software.
name: Siphon AI
title: Siphon AI

api_list.name: Search
api_list.description: Search and Get Results from Major Search Engines

optional_parameters.name: google_domain
optional_parameters.description:
Specify which google domain you'd like to use.
Available domains here: https://www.google.com/supported_domains

By default: google.com
